'''Fernanda Cama Pereira Lima''' ({{IPA-pt|fe<U+027E><U+02C8>n<U+0250><U+0303>d<U+0250> <U+02C8>k<U+0250><U+0303>m<U+0250> pe<U+02C8><U+027E>ej<U+027E><U+0250> <U+02C8><U+026B><U+0129>m<U+0250>}}, born June 25, 1977) is a [[Brazil]]ian [[actress]], [[Model (person)|model]] and [[television host]]. With a short career in [[film]] an [[telenovela]]s, she has established herself as a host on  [[MTV Brasil]], [[Rede TV!]] and [[Globo TV]]. She has been contracted by [[FIFA]] as the [[muse]] of the [[2014 FIFA World Cup]] an the [[FIFA Ballon d'Or]].

==Biography==
===Model===
One of three children - she has two brothers - of two professors of [[physical education]], as a child, she showed interest in [[journalism]] and the art world, creating [[choreographies]] prepared at parties and family gatherings. She also went to the streets with her cousins <U+200B><U+200B>carrying cameras to do research on voting at election, editing the material recorded at home.<ref name="oficial">{{citar web|url=http://www.fernandalima.com.br/site/index.html|title=DeOndeVim|publisher=SiteOficial|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> She began her modeling career at the age 14, when she was discovered by a [[photographer]],<ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.glitztv.com.br/noticias-br/fernanda-lima/|title=Fernanda Lima|publisher=Glitz|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> and she ended up living for five months in [[Japan]], [[Milan]], and [[Zurich]] in 1990 as a teenager.<ref name="revista">{{citar web|url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/revista/rf2311200309.htm|title=Fernanda Lima|publisher=Revista da Folha|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> When she returned to in [[Brazil]], she moved to [[S<U+00E3>o Paulo]]. As a model, in Brazil and abroad, she has been photographed for dozens of covers and fashion editorials in publications such as ''[[L'Officiel]]'', ''[[I-D]]'', ''[[Nova]]'', ''[[Marie Claire]]'', ''[[Elle (magazine)|Elle]]'', ''[[GQ]]'', ''Trip'',<ref name="oficial"/> among others, and advertising campaigns for the ''[[Benetton Group]]'' in [[Italy]].<ref name=quem>{{citar web|url=http://revistaquem.globo.com/Revista/Quem/0,,ERT84648-9530,00.html|title=Fernanda Lima|publisher=Quem|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref>

===Television===
In 1999 she made <U+200B><U+200B>her television debut on MTV Brazil, in ''Mochil<U+00E3>o MTV''.<ref name=ig/> While making this program, she went to [[Hawaii]], it was there where she decided to study [[Communications]] and she went back to [[Sao Paulo]], where she attended and graduated in [[Journalism]] from [[Centro Universit<U+00E1>rio das Faculdades Metropolitanas Unidas]].<ref name="oficial"/><ref name=ig>{{citar web|url=http://gente.ig.com.br/fernandalima/#topoBiografia|title=Fernanda Lima|publisher=IG Gente|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> In the same year, she went to work for [[RedeTV!]], debuting in the channel on November presenting two programs, ''Interligado'', which ws aimed at a young audience and conveyed video clips and music and topics of interest to teens, and ''TV Escolha'',<ref name=ig/> a movie session transmitted on Sundays and where viewers chose the films that would be shown.

After nine months in RedeTV!, she was invited to return to her previous channel and, in August 2000, she again presented the ''Mochil<U+00E3>o MTV'', ''[[Luau MTV]]'', and ''Fica Comigo'',<ref name=ig/> which premiered in October of that year. In February 2005, she was hired by [[Rede Globo]] to replace [[Ang<U+00E9>lica (presenter)|Ang<U+00E9>lica]] of ''V<U+00ED>deo Game'', presenting the program  ''[[V<U+00ED>deo Show]]'',  during [[pregnancy]] and [[maternity leave]] of the titular host.<ref name=ig/> Soon after, she was invited to act in the telenovela ''[[Bang Bang (telenovela)|Bang Bang]]'', set in a plot of city directly reflecting the old west [[Brazil]], where she was the protagonist Diana Bullock. Without any training or experience in [[drama]], she accepted the role, taking lessons [[martial arts]] and hiring a [[speech therapist]]. Due to being inexperienced for the lead role, her portrayal of the character received several criticisms from the press, who said she was the cause of the low ratings of the telenovela.<ref name=quem/> In spite of the criticisms, she was invited to play role in ''[[P<U+00E9> na Jaca]]'' by Carlos Lombardi playing the role of ''Maria Bo''. She got better reviews from the viewers.<ref name=quem/> She got other roles in ''[[Fant<U+00E1>stico]]'', ''Daqui para Frente'', and ''Por Toda Minha Vida''.<ref name=ig/> In August 2009, she began hosting ''Amor & Sexo'', which is aimed at a young audience talks about the theme of [[sex]] and related topics.<ref>{{citar web|url=http://tvg.globo.com/programas/amor-e-sexo/|title=Amor&Sexo|publisher=Rede Globo|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref>  

===="Muse" the 2014 World Cup====
[[File:Fernanda_Lima_WorldCup_Crop.jpg|thumb|150px|Fernanda during the draw for the [[FIFA World Cup 2014]].]]
She was contracted by [[FIFA]] in July 2010 to present alongside her husband [[Rodrigo Hilbert]] during the launching the emblem of the 2014 World Cup in Brazil directly from [[South Africa]]. In July 2011, with presenter Tadeu Schmidt, she hosted the draw of the [[2014 World Cup Qualifiers]].<ref>{{citar web|url=http://trivela.uol.com.br/mundo/acusacao-de-racismo-tem-muito-a-ver-com-modus-operandi-da-fifa|title=Acusa<U+00E7><U+00E3>o de racismo tem muito a ver com modus operandi da Fifa|last=Lobo|first=Felipe|publisher=TrivelaUOL|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> In December 2013, again alongside her husband, she presented the drawing of lots of the World Cup.<ref>{{citar web|URL=http://esportes.terra.com.br/futebol/copa-2014/ao-lado-do-marido-fernanda-lima-arranca-suspiros-e-dribla-nervosismo,da1a674dbe8c2410VgnVCM4000009bcceb0aRCRD.html|title=Ao lado do marido, Fernanda Lima arranca suspiros e dribla nervosismo|author=Terra|accessdate=06/12/2013}}</ref> Her participation in this event was seen live by more than 500 million viewers in 200 countries around the world,<ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.estadao.com.br/noticias/esportes,sorteio-dos-grupos-da-copa-sera-visto-por-500-milhoes-de-telespectadores,1104278,0.htm|title=Sorteio dos grupos da Copa ser<U+00E1> visto por 500 milh<U+00F5>es de telespectadores|publisher=OESP|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> Causing her to be called the "[[goddess]]" or "[[mus]]e" of the World Cup by the foreign media.<ref>{{citar web|url=http://webmedia.newseum.org/newseum-multimedia/dfp/pdf7/ECUA_HOY.pdf|title=Fernanda Lima se rob<U+00F4> eu show de sorteo|publisher=Hoy|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref><ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.clarin.com/deportes/Fernanda-Lima-presento-sorteo-Mundial_0_1042696119.html|title=Qui<U+00E9>n es Fernanda Lima, la diosa que present<U+00F3> el sorteo del Mundial|publisher=Clarin|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref><ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2519538/Brazilian-TV-hostess-Fernanda-Lima-steals-10-people-second-tweet-World-Cup-draw.html|title=Brazilian TV hostess steals the show as 10 people per second tweet about lovely Lima |publisher=Daily Mail|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref>

The neckline of the dress worn by Fernanda during the presentation of the draw was censored in the live broadcast of the event in [[Iran]], one of the qualified countries of the World Cup. AThe authorities of the country - which has cultural and religious restrictions to women's clothing and where women can not go to football games - suspended transmission in real time<ref>{{citar web|url=http://blogs.estadao.com.br/jamil-chade/2013/12/08/sorteio-da-copa-foi-censurado-no-ira/|title=Sorteio da Copa foi censurado no Ir<U+00E3>|last=Chade|first=Jamil|publisher=O Estado de S<U+00E3>o Paulo|accessdate=09/12/2013}}</ref>

At the end of 2013, she was included in a list of 10 Brazilians who stood out in the international news that year, prepared by [[BBC Brasil]].<ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/portuguese/noticias/2013/12/131231_brasileiros_noticianomundo_pai.shtml?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|title=Dez brasileiros que foram not<U+00ED>cia no mundo em 2013|publisher=BBC Brasil|accessdate=01/01/2014}}</ref> In January 2014, she was the official host of the [[FIFA Ballon d'Or|Ballon d'Or]] of [[FIFA]] for  Dutch football player [[Ruud Gullit]].<ref>{{citar web|url=http://oglobo.globo.com/esportes/acompanhe-disputa-da-bola-de-ouro-da-fifa-11286422|title=Acompanhe a disputa da Bola de Ouro da Fifa  |publisher=O Globo|accessdate=13/01/2014}}</ref> Because of the huge publicity around Fernanda, she was invited to perform in [[London]] during the [[National Television Awards]], the highest award of the British television.<ref>[http://f5.folha.uol.com.br/celebridades/2014/01/1401474-chamada-de-glamorosa-e-bonita-fernanda-lima-apresenta-premiacao-em-londres.shtml Chamada de glamurosa e bonita, Fernanda Lima apresenta pr<U+00EA>mio em Londres]</ref>

==Personal life==
Fernanda is married to fellow actor and model [[Rodrigo Hilbert]], whom she met at a [[luau]] in [[Ipanema]], in [[Rio de Janeiro]],<ref name=quem/> with whom he has twin sons John and Francis.<ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.terra.com.br/istoegente/edicoes/451/artigo78767-1.htm|title=A chegada dos g<U+00EA>meos|publisher=Isto<U+00C9> Gente|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> She is a fan of  [[Gr<U+00EA>mio Football Porto Alegrense]],<ref>{{citar web|url=http://www.portalpower.com.br/gatas/fernanda-lima-e-musa-do-gremio/|title=Fernanda Lima <U+00E9> musa do Gr<U+00EA>mio|publisher=Portalpower|accessdate=08/12/2013}}</ref> a business partner in a restaurant in [[S<U+00E3>o Paulo]], a [[vegetarian]], and a practitioner of [[yoga]].

